  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们今天来画一下MyFitnessFriend的系统上下文图吧。核心是一个健身营养追踪平台，用户可以在上面记录饮食、喝水、运动，还能查看自己的进度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mff",
        "user"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那用户和平台之间的交互具体包括哪些？比如只是浏览，还是有实际的数据录入？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "mff"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用户会记录三餐、饮水量、运动数据，还能看日记和打卡 streaks。所以关系应该是\"记录饮食、喝水、运动；查看日记与打卡\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "mff",
        "Rel(user, mff)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把用户和MyFitnessFriend系统之间的这条关系线加上了。接下来身份验证怎么处理？自建还是第三方？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "mff"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们用Clerk做身份验证，支持Google OAuth登录。Clerk会签发JWT令牌，我们的平台负责验证令牌和获取用户身份。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "clerk",
        "mff",
        "user"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有两条关系需要确认：一是用户直接通过Google OAuth登录Clerk，二是MFF平台向Clerk验证JWT。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "clerk",
        "mff"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，用户那边标注\"通过Google OAuth认证\"，MFF到Clerk是\"验证JWT令牌，获取用户身份\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rel(user, clerk)",
        "Rel(mff, clerk)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Clerk外部系统，以及这两条关系线。还有一个问题，食物营养数据从哪来？自建数据库吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "clerk",
        "foodApi"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不，我们接外部API，比如Edamam那种食物数据库。用户扫条形码或者搜索食物名称时，MFF要去查这个外部接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "foodApi",
